      "content_latex": "Example 27\n\nExpand and simplify:\n\n(a) $-\\sqrt{2}(\\sqrt{2} + 3)$\n\n(b) $-\\sqrt{3}(4 - \\sqrt{3})$\n\nAnswer\n\n(a) $-\\sqrt{2}(\\sqrt{2} + 3) = -\\sqrt{2} \\times \\sqrt{2} + (-\\sqrt{2}) \\times 3 = -2 - 3\\sqrt{2}$\n\n(b) $-\\sqrt{3}(4 - \\sqrt{3}) = -\\sqrt{3} \\times 4 + (-\\sqrt{3}) \\times (-\\sqrt{3}) = -4\\sqrt{3} + 3$",
